latestPosts.caption:
Last birthday before I get married to the love of my life🌚❤️

So chaliye shuru se shuru karte h
Birthday start hone p I was super duper sad. Ek to waise hi meri last diwali and birthday tha to uska gum. Upar se zero plans for birthday and I was feeling so low. Fir @areybhaisahab ne call kark bola ki bahar kyu ni ja rahe h hum. Aur isk baad @vidhi__vashishth ji se salah mashwara karne k baad hmara plan bn gya. Thoda mood bhi better ho gya. 
Fir subah subah pooja path karne k baad mere pitaji mera cake lekar aaye. AND THAT WAS THE BEST CAKE EVER!!!!

He googled a picture of bridal doli and vo pic ka reference dekar cake bnwa k laye h😭😭😭😭❤️❤️❤️❤️
Bohot hi zyada thoughtful. Totally unexpected but so so soooo beautiful. 

Aur fir m aur mere dost including khushi🥲
Hum gaye gtb nagar
Kha pikar aur khub sara dance kark aa gaye. 
Aaj ki highlight to cake hi tha but aaj ek baat samjh aayi. Ki jo hota h sach me ache k liye hi hota h. Start bhale hi bekar hua ho lekin end to bohot badia hua h. 

Aur han special thanks to @areybhaisahab and @jigyasa.jain_16 for writing such a cute and long birthday wish for me❤️

Aur jitne bhi logo ne aaj mujhe wish kiya un sabko ek bohot badi jhappi❤️❤️❤️

Happy diwali and thank you agar yaha tak pada to. Comments me ek blue dil daal dena🥹🥰❤️

latestPosts.caption:
💅✨RANT & READY✨💅

Welcome to my new series where I Rant while getting ready. And in the first episode I am sharing a major life crisis which we are facing RN🥲
But makeup kaafi acha hua so +1 for that😎

Let me know your honest opinions on this video as I have never ever opened up like this before and its very sad yet funny to share my vulnerable life🥲🙏 So yeah please lmk💖

Bought this amazing dress and it fits like a glove😍

Comment for link

Mera sasural❤️🧿

Last week was a roller coaster of emotions as my in laws visited us for Ikshu’s Kuan Poojan. Mujhe full choti bahu wali vibes aayi is baar and sab k saath itna zyada maza kiya. Puri family ek saath thi except my Nanad ji aur unki kami hame kaafi pata chali😭 but overall it was so so good. 
Also hamare pyaare bhaiya ne Karjat me ek holiday home banaya jiske name k inauguration par hum sab log gaye and the name is @barnali.bliss . Itna cozy setup kiya h unhone and I cant wait to stay there. 

All in all it was a great week and now I am missing everyone a lot to bas isiliye yeh bina AI wala caption hehe. 

Okbye🙈🧿
